an></li> --><!-- <li><a href=\"/book/book.php?lang=cn&pr_id=104\" class=\"ask\"></a><a href=\"/order/order.php?id=12&pr_id=104\" class=\"order\"></a></li> --></p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `bees_product` VALUES ('53', '', null, '20', '<p>\r\n	产品可增加网部纤维和其它湿部助剂留着,加快网部的滤水和干部的脱水。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	一般说来,大分子量的聚合物有更好的助留性能,小分子量的聚合物有较好的助滤性能。</p>\r\n', null, null, null, null, '<div id=\"body\" jquery1355572997109=\"32\">\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><strong>※</strong></span></span>技术指标</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">产品外观:&nbsp; 白色颗粒</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"display: none\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">固含量: &gt;90%</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;分子量:&nbsp;500～800万</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">溶解时间: &lt;60分钟</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;PH值: 4～7</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">※使用方法及注意事项</span></span></strong></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">1</span><span style=\"color: black\">、将该分散剂配制成0.1-0.5%浓度溶液使用。将一公斤分散剂均匀撒入一吨水中，注意要一边搅拌一边撒入，溶解1小时后经过40目筛网过滤配成稀溶液备用，使用时再用3-5倍的水稀释。 </span></span></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">2</span><span style=\"color: black\">、加入时应尽量靠网前添加，添加在网箱、沉沙盘或高位箱处都可，但直接用等同于网箱宽度的滴管加入网箱效果最佳，用阀门控制流量。 </span></span></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">3</span><span style=\"color: black\">、一般来说，吨纸的用量为500-1500ppm,但根据所生产的纸张不同和加入填料的不同也有所差异。</span></span></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">4、<font size=\"2\">本品无毒，注意防潮、防雨，在储运过程中防止高温与曝晒</font>。</span></span></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin: 7.05pt 0cm\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: black\">5、<font size=\"2\">储存温度以 0-35 ℃为宜</font>。</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"body\" jquery1355572997109=\"34\" style=\"display: none\">\r\n	<div id=\"body\" jquery1355571001296=\"34\" style=\"display: block\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">※包装规格</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">常规包装是每袋25公斤。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">※包装材料</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">包装材质是纸塑复合。</span></span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">干粉型造纸助留剂是一种集助留助滤剂为一体的新型高效造纸专用助剂,属于有机高分子聚合物,它能</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">1、显著提高纸浆中细小纤维和填料的留着率,节省纤维,降低原料成本。</span></span></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">2、更好的细小纤维、胶体、填料等的留着,可以保证和改善纸张的品质。</span></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">3、降低白水浓度,减少白水含固率,从而减少白水回收装置及污水处理厂的负荷。</span></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">4、提高网部脱水速率,从而使进一步提高车速或降低蒸汽消耗成为可能。</span></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">5、改善网毯清洁度,延长网毯的使用效能和使用周期。</span></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">6、&nbsp;可有效改善纸张施胶度,降低施胶剂的用量。</span></span></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">7、减少系统沉积物,帮助清除系统的有害物质,提高纸机运行性能。</span></span></div>\r\n');
